Name: Problems and Solutions for Mcquarrie's Quantum Chemistry

ReviewList.Text: Detailed, answers every question in at the end of each chapter. Very helpful. I did not give it five starts because it there are some questions that leave unanswered questions. But for the most part this is a great study helper.
This book is really helpful and really great for studying! I purchased it and have been using it ever since.
It is a very useful book to beginners learning Quantum Chemistry.
This book is a wonderful tool to improve the learning of quantum chemistry. There are several interesting discussions and helpful chapters dealing with math concepts.
